{"meta":{"title":"Graphe","subtitle":"","description":"","author":"Graphecyt","url":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"tages","date":"2022-10-17T10:27:04.000Z","updated":"2022-10-17T10:28:22.983Z","comments":false,"path":"tages/index.html","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/tages/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"about","date":"2020-02-23T11:20:33.000Z","updated":"2022-10-17T10:30:04.866Z","comments":false,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"categories","date":"2022-10-17T10:32:45.000Z","updated":"2022-10-17T10:33:39.874Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"我的第一篇博客.md","slug":"我的第一篇博客-md","date":"2022-10-17T10:36:44.000Z","updated":"2022-10-17T12:50:54.526Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/10/17/我的第一篇博客-md/","link":"","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/2022/10/17/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2-md/","excerpt":"","text":"一级标题代码测试： 1print(&quot;Hello&quot;) 注意：这里因为我放在md文件中的，所以加上了\\，不解析```，实际测试时请去掉\\。 图片测试： 引用测试： 这是一条引用 二级标题无序列表测试： 哈哈 嘿嘿 吼吼 三级标题四级标题 3.1dropdown 下拉 布局思路1.上面 全部商品分类 和下面列表应该在一个dropdown div里面 宽度一样 命名：上面dt 下面dd2.下拉菜单用列表 ul&gt;li 来做 大盒子dd给定宽高背景 红色3.li设置左margin：2px 里面文字有一定距离 pdding-left：10px 文字居中4.hover做法 碰到li变色5.后面箭头用after做 12345678910111213141516171819202122&lt;div class=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;dt&quot;&gt;全部商品分类&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=&quot;dd&quot;&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;家用电器&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;手机、数码、通信&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;电脑、办公&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;家居、家具、家装、厨具&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;男装、女装、童装、内衣&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;个户化妆、清洁用品、宠物&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;鞋靴、箱包、珠宝、奢侈品&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;运动户外、钟表&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;汽车、汽车用品&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;母婴、玩具乐器&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;食品、酒类、生鲜、特产&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;医药保健&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;图书、音像、电子书&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;彩票、旅行、充值、票务&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;理财、众筹、白条、保险&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 小li做法1.marfin-left 2px 为了点以后左边留红 美观 12345678.dropdown .dd ul li &#123; position: relative; margin-left: 2px; height: 31px; line-height: 31px; padding-left: 10px; color: #fff;&#125; 箭头做法 伪元素1、用绝对定位 absolute2.相对于父亲是li li加相对定位relarive 12345678.dropdown .dd ul li::after &#123; position: absolute; top: 1px; right: 10px; font-family: &#x27;icomoon&#x27;; content: &#x27;\\e920&#x27;; font-size: 14px;&#125; 3.2navitems 做法思路： 为了增大链接选项 1.设置ul 左浮动 2.ul里放a a为行内元素 给a转为inline-block 给padding撑开a的范围（左右距离各一半25） 用户鼠标放在盒子上有链接 1234567.navitems ul li a &#123; display: block; padding: 0 25px; line-height: 45px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500;&#125;","categories":[{"name":"一级分类","slug":"一级分类","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/categories/%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/"},{"name":"二级分类","slug":"一级分类/二级分类","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/categories/%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/"}],"tags":[{"name":"第一篇","slug":"第一篇","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/tags/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87/"},{"name":"测试","slug":"测试","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/tags/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/"}]},{"title":"ww","slug":"ww","date":"2022-10-17T10:15:33.000Z","updated":"2022-10-17T10:21:58.759Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/10/17/ww/","link":"","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/2022/10/17/ww/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux学习","slug":"Linux学习","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/tags/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"}]},{"title":"paper","slug":"paper","date":"2022-10-14T13:22:41.000Z","updated":"2022-10-14T13:22:41.903Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/10/14/paper/","link":"","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/2022/10/14/paper/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[],"tags":[]}],"categories":[{"name":"一级分类","slug":"一级分类","permalink":"http://yigeyouzia.github.io/categories/%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E7%B1%B